1" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=pubmed&amp;article-id=529455&amp;issue-id=10201&amp;journal-id=39&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Entrez%7CPubMed%7CRecord">PubMed</a>] [<a href="//dx.doi.org/10.1191%2F0969733002ne522oa" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=529455&amp;issue-id=10201&amp;journal-id=39&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CCrosslink%7CDOI">CrossRef</a>] <span class="nowrap">[<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Nurs+Ethics&amp;title=Development+of+a+model+of+moral+distress+in+military+nursing&amp;author=ST+Fry&amp;author=RM+Harvey&amp;author=AC+Hurley&amp;author=BJ+Foley&amp;volume=9&amp;publication_year=2002&amp;pages=373-387&amp;pmid=12219401&amp;doi=10.1191/0969733002ne522oa&amp;" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=529455&amp;issue-id=10201&amp;journal-id=39&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CLink%7CGoogle%20Scholar">Google Scholar</a>]</span></span></li><li id="B15"><span class="citation">Hamric A. Moral distress in everyday ethics. <span><span class="ref-journal">Nurs Outlook. </span>2002;<span class="ref-vol">48</span>:199\xe2\x80\x93201. doi: 10.1067/mno.2000.110564.</span> [<a href="/pubmed/11044292" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=pubmed&amp;article-id=529455&amp;issue-id=10201&amp;journal-id=39&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Entrez%7CPubMed%7CRecord">PubMed</a>] [<a href="//dx.doi.org/10.1067%2Fmno.2000.110564" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=529455&amp;issue-id=10201&amp;journal-id=39&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CCrosslink%7CDOI">CrossRef</a>] <span class="nowrap">[<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Nurs+Outlook&amp;title=Moral+distress+in+everyday+ethics&amp;author=A+Hamric&amp;volume=48&amp;publication_year=2002&amp;pages=199-201&amp;pmid=11044292&amp;doi=10.1067/mno.2000.110564&amp;" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=529455&amp;issue-id=10201&